---
title: Lamb Meatballs & Veggie Traybake with Roast Veggies & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: There’s no fuss when you can make dinner on a tray and leave it in the oven to cook to perfection. Meatballs are flavoured in our favourite Nan’s seasoning and the veggies are roasted right beside them. Dollop with herby mayo to pull everything together.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*

